OL,3,CMetro hits maintenance firm with fines
OL,4,Cover train failures
OL,6,FThe firm responsible for getting the
OL,7,FTyne and Wear Metro's troubled trains
OL,8,Finto service every day has been fined
OL,9,Fmore than #1m for under-performance.
OL,11,FMetro operator Nexus has confirmed
OL,12,Fthat it has hit Swiss manufacturer
OL,13,FStadler with financial penalties for
OL,14,Fnot having enough carriages in a
OL,15,Fusable state over the past year.
OL,17,FThe rail network has been beset with
OL,18,Fproblems over recent months, with
OL,19,Fpassengers left increasingly
OL,20,Ffrustrated by regular delays and
OL,21,Fcancellations.
