OL,3,CMetro hits maintenance firm with fines
OL,4,Cover train failures
OL,6,FThe Metro's existing trains have been
OL,7,Fin service for more than 40 years and
OL,8,Fare becoming increasingly failure-
OL,9,Fprone.
OL,11,FBefore Christmas, the Metro slumped to
OL,12,Fits worst ever performance level `
OL,13,Fwith only 61% of services arriving on
OL,14,Ftime in the four weeks up to 9
OL,15,FDecember.
OL,17,FAnd there has since been bad news on
OL,18,Fthe long-awaited arrival of the #362
OL,19,Fmillion new Metro fleet being built by
OL,20,FStadler, which has
