OL,3,CMetro hits maintenance firm with fines
OL,4,Cover train failures
OL,6,FStadler is contracted to maintain the
OL,7,FMetro's current fleet as well as
OL,8,Fbuilding the new one, with 28 trains
OL,9,Frequired to run a normal weekday
OL,10,Fservice.
OL,12,FIn figures released following a
OL,13,Frequest by the Local Democracy
OL,14,FReporting Service, Nexus has now
OL,15,Fconfirmed that it has so far withheld
OL,16,F#1.4m from Stadler in 2023/24 for not
OL,17,Fgetting enough of the existing trains
OL,18,Favailable for use in the last 12
OL,19,Fmonths.
