OL,3,CMetro hits maintenance firm with fines
OL,4,Cover train failures
OL,6,FThe contractual penalties are issued
OL,7,Fon an ongoing basis as shortages
OL,8,Fhappen throughout the year and it is
OL,9,Funderstood that the situation has
OL,10,Fworsened in the latter half of the
OL,11,Fyear, with the cold weather during
OL,12,Fwinter months playing havoc with the
OL,13,Ftrains' ageing components.
OL,15,FA Nexus spokesperson said: "The Metro
OL,16,Ffleet is more than 43 years old and is
OL,17,Foperating beyond its lifespan. We
OL,18,Fcontinue to work closely with Stadler
OL,19,Fto maintain Metro train availability
OL,20,Fwhile we transition to the new fleet.
