OL,6,F"The contract that we have with
OL,7,FStadler provides for financial
OL,8,Fadjustments where performance falls
OL,9,Fbelow levels that the contract
OL,10,Frequires.
OL,12,F"Payments to Stadler have therefore
OL,13,Fbeen reduced, commensurate with the
OL,14,Fperformance that they have delivered,
OL,15,Fin accordance with contractual terms."
