OL,6,FGerman firm DB Regio, which was
OL,7,Fresponsible for the running of the
OL,8,Fentire Metro network rather than just
OL,9,Ftrains' maintenance, was previously
OL,10,Fhit with fines totalling around #2m by
OL,11,FNexus between 2010 and 2017, before
OL,12,FNexus took the day-to-day operation of
OL,13,Fthe network back into its own hands.
OL,15,FA spokesperson from Stadler said: "The
OL,16,FTyne and Wear Metro fleet that Stadler
OL,17,Flooks after is 43 years old and trains
OL,18,Fhave reached their life expectancy.
